<section xml:id="welcome">
  <title>Welcome to IMS2</title>
  
  <p>
    This is the PreTeXt version of <em>Introduction to Modern Statistics</em>, Second Edition by Mine Çetinkaya-Rundel and Johanna Hardin.
    This PreTeXt conversion is hosted at <url href="https://PreTeXtBooks.github.io/ims/">https://pretextbooks.github.io/ims/</url>.
    Introduction to Modern Statistics, which we'll refer to as IMS going forward, is a textbook from the <url href="https://www.openintro.org/">OpenIntro</url> project.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    The original book website is available at <url href="https://openintro-ims.netlify.app/">https://openintro-ims.netlify.app/</url>, where it will always be available for free.
    It is also available in PDF (for free or for the amount you choose to contribute) on Leanpub and in black and white paperback for purchase for $25.
  </p>
  
